Title: Sight Unseen
Plot: The team returns to Earth with a piece of technology that allows them to see alien creatures everywhere, and must attempt to contain the problem when it spreads beyond the base.
GuestStars: Betty Linde, Michael Karl Richards, Raimund Stamm, Jennifer Steede, Jacob Chaos, Brad Dryborough, Jacquie Janzen, Jody Raicot, Katina Robillard
